00:32:40.020 --> 00:32:42.210
of the Earth around the Sun.

00:32:42.210 --> 00:32:44.100
But Newton ignored all of that,

00:32:44.100 --> 00:32:48.450
all he looked at was just a
single parameter, essentially,

00:32:48.450 --> 00:32:50.100
the mass of the Earth.

00:32:50.100 --> 00:32:52.290
And with that, he could
correctly, for the most part,

00:32:52.290 --> 00:32:54.510
predict how the Earth was
