00:36:01.050 --> 00:36:04.350
what you're seeing most of
the time is small events.

00:36:04.350 --> 00:36:08.250
And this can lull you into
a false sense of security,

00:36:08.250 --> 00:36:10.260
you think you understand
how things are going.

