00:37:50.460 --> 00:37:53.880
So venture capital is a world
that depends on taking risks

00:37:53.880 --> 00:37:57.150
in the hope that you'll get a
few of these extreme outliers

00:37:57.150 --> 00:37:58.890
which outperform all of the rest

00:37:58.890 --> 00:38:00.900
of the investments combined.

00:38:00.900 --> 00:38:03.540
- [Derek] Book publishers
